1%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258E%2592%25E9%2599%25A4%25E5%2590%2591%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E9%259B%2586%25E8%25B3%2587%25E3%2580%25802009%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%259B%25BE12%25E4%25BE%259B5%25E3%2580%258C%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%25B4%2580%25E4%25BE%259B%25E8%2582%25A1%25E3%2580%258D&d=8aZ3B%2FsgtJclBbEiVdGGE28KfKULefuOMk0AcQ9dAAw%3D&h=705e1b3b\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2607192/%E3%80%90%E6%BB%99%E8%B1%90%E4%B8%8D%E6%B4%BE%E6%81%AF%E3%80%91%E6%BB%99%E8%B1%90%E7%A8%B1%E4%B8%8D%E6%8E%92%E9%99%A4%E5%90%91%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E9%9B%86%E8%B3%87%E3%80%802009%E5%B9%B4%E6%9B%BE12%E4%BE%9B5%E3%80%8C%E4%B8%96%E7%B4%80%E4%BE%9B%E8%82%A1%E3%80%8D</a>"},{"pid":"d07f240e4aa41f99f83818be639ada20aad55315","tid":2196575,"uid":167585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c77450745317ae6437a5945a6fbbb75fc550687b","tid":2196575,"uid":167585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T04:44:55.000Z","msg":"【滙豐不派息】滙豐稱不排除向市場集資　2009年曾12供5「世紀供股」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2607192/%E3%80%90%E6%BB%99%E8%B1%90%E4%B8%8D%E6%B4%BE%E6%81%AF%E3%80%91%E6%BB%99%E8%B1%90%E7%A8%B1%E4%B8%8D%E6%8E%92%E9%99%A4%E5%90%91%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E9%9B%86%E8%B3%87%E3%80%802009%E5%B9%B4%E6%9B%BE12%E4%BE%9B5%E3%80%8C%E4%B8%96%E7%B4%80%E4%BE%9B%E8%82%A1%E3%80%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2607192%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%25BB%2599%25E8%25B1%2590%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E6%2581%25AF%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%25BB%2599%25E8%25B1%2590%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258E%2592%25E9%2599%25A4%25E5%2590%2591%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E9%259B%2586%25E8%25B3%2587%25E3%2580%25802009%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%259B%25BE12%25E4%25BE%259B5%25E3%2580%258C%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%25B4%2580%25E4%25BE%259B%25E8%2582%25A1%25E3%2580%258D&d=8aZ3B%2FsgtJclBbEiVdGGE28KfKULefuOMk0AcQ9dAAw%3D&h=705e1b3b\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2607192/%E3%80%90%E6%BB%99%E8%B1%90%E4%B8%8D%E6%B4%BE%E6%81%AF%E3%80%91%E6%BB%99%E8%B1%90%E7%A8%B1%E4%B8%8D%E6%8E%92%E9%99%A4%E5%90%91%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E9%9B%86%E8%B3%87%E3%80%802009%E5%B9%B4%E6%9B%BE12%E4%BE%9B5%E3%80%8C%E4%B8%96%E7%B4%80%E4%BE%9B%E8%82%A1%E3%80%8D</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T04:46:27.000Z","msg":"二、什麼是供股<br />\n<br />\n「供股」是上市公司最常用的集資方式之一，其籌集資金的對象是面向所有股東。供股是根據股權持倉的數量按照供股價格購買對應數量的正股。<br />\n<br />\n以最近宣佈供股的$國泰航空(<a href=\"http://00293.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00293.HK&d=8aZ3B%2FsgtJclBbEiVdGGE28KfKULefuOMk0AcQ9dAAw%3D&h=e0d4b6b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00293.HK</a>)$為例，根據公司公告，按於供股記錄日期每持有11股現有股份獲發7股供股股份的基準，按供股認購價4.68港元進行供股2,503,355,631股供股股份，集資總金額為約117億港元。<br />\n<br />\n但值得注意的是，通常上市公司會折價供股，然後股價必然會向下調整。<br />\n<br />\n詳細來説！<br />\n<br />\n若上市公司當前的已發行股數1億股，現股價(除權日前收盤價)每股1港元。公司宣佈了1供10的方案，「供股價」只有0.1港元，即新股折價90%來集資，集資目標是1億港元。<br />\n<br />\n假設所有股東參與了供股，那麼在除權日後，公司的股份會從1億股變成11億股(1億舊股+10億新供的股份)。理論上，除權後股價應該會變成0.182港元，比除權前的1港元暴跌82%。<br />\n<br />\n當然，最怕的是股東什麼操作都不做，那麼手上的股票會馬上貶值。<br />\n<br />\n現有股東不願意參與「供股」，最好趕緊賣掉股份，或是賣掉「供股權」，否則一旦過了除權日，就得眼睜睜地看着自己的股票每股價格從1港元變成0.182港元。<br />\n<br />\n另外説到供股，自然容易聯想到合股，曾經不乏公司通過不斷的合股再「供股」的方式，來迷惑小股民，大家需要多多警惕。"},{"pid":"f8ef58bbfde05c2c39a90de8f15fc5e99ef62ffe","tid":2196575,"uid":337910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b999673937ed234e5c4f826ab5cc5f50dab7893b","tid":2196575,"uid":167585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"581ffb0a2147fe6bfe1d734adbb158feaa32f432","tid":2196575,"uid":65928,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T04:37:06.000Z","msg":"人棄我取<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nAll in 00005<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T04:42:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\